cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.DS 

This paper presents a learning-based approach for control of uncertain linear systems, which involves the use of historical data to approximate the safe set and value function. This work is relevant to the fields of control theory (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and data science (cs.DS).
